i just got out of my first class.math. it was so incredibly boring already. my teacher is literally at least 70 and the class doesnt involve math...its so weird.i randomly get a bar of reception so i pretty much cant text anyone so ill just be sitting there in my own little la la world. i have bio then psych in 30 mins. not sure yet if ill get into bio but hopefully i will. alright gotta go eat with tasheckka.

I hurt myself today 
To see if I still feel 
I focus on the pain 
The only thing that's real 
The needle tears a hole
The old familiar sting 
Try to kill it all away 
But I remember everything 

What have I become 
My sweetest friend 
Everyone I know goes away 
In the end 
And you could have it all 
My empire of dirt 
I will let you down 
I will make you hurt 

I wear this crown of thorns 
Upon my liar's chair 
Full of broken thoughts 
I cannot repair 
Beneath the stains of time 
The feelings disappear 
You are someone else 
I am still right here 

What have I become 
My sweetest friend

i just got back from seeing hostel with jessica. that movie was seriously disturbing. i definitely would not see that movie again, it was just too creepy.that crap could actually happen so that makes it 10 times worse. it was nice catching up with jessica though. we had some starbs and taco bell.it was so good.oh ya while we were walking to the movie we saw this lady on the ground handcuffed with 2 cops holding her down. one of the cops was holding a freakin stunn gun that he apparently used. it was insane and we were kind of afraid cuz some random lady was getting arrested. that was pretty much my fun-filled night

all i did today was lay in bed...seriously.once again i had el pollo for dinner and it was rather yummy as usual.i'm gradually cuttin back on my dinner since ive been binging horribly lately.why i dont know but i had 2 brc's and a cheese quesadilla...thats still so much food for dinner.eh oh well.better luck tomorrow.
why is it that the hairdresser is more supportive of my wanting to be an animal cop than my parents are? thats just sad
i never knew 4-wheeling was so much fun.

Sparky your in a better place im sure well at least i hope.At least your not in any pain which is good.We put you out of your misery so you would finally feel better...we couldnt be selfish by trying to keep you here for longer.It was for the best.You'll always know how much we loved you and it wasnt an easy decision on whether to give you medication to see if you lets would be ok or if we should just put you out of your pain.I think we picked the right choice for you.Even though its killing me it was still the right thing to do for you.You deserved to be out of your pain and we couldnt keep you alive just for us.I really hope that it wasnt painful for you to die.I dont think it was but i just really hope it wasnt.It was horrible for me to watch your legs and arms to move while you were passing on.It was horrible when i close my eyes thats what i see your muscles relaxing and your bladder emptying.I cant get it out of my head, you were my brother and best friend.Im gonna miss you so much but you'll always be around,in our heart and memories and in the urn.I want to put it on the refrigerator but dad says no so you'll probably go in the garage where you always were.Im just really going to miss you and no matter how old i am i'll always remember you.You were my first dog and you made my love for animals stronger.I love you Sparky and i'll never forget you.

your sister,
Katrina

Today I got my report card in the mail.I was soooo afraid of getting a D or F in chem and a C in PE.I was really happy when I found out i got a C- in Chem and Gipe actually gave me an A.I was shocked I didnt believe my report card was right but hey it works for me.Now i get a new car since i got all A's,B's and C's so no more van.My mom was like "if we get you a new car are you going to go and kill yourself in it" and i was like "what?? who said i was going to kill myself in the car" and she was like "well if you are gonna kill yourself in the car we'll keep the van and you can do it in there."I can't believe my mom actually said that.Geez I knew she wouldnt care if i killed myself but ya know what I dont care if i do either.Last night I was talking to ms.spencer and it was really wierd she was actually talking to me about my cutting but then my stupid time was up so i had to go.It was a wierd conversation though.well im off to eat even though im not hungry.Audi
